[thinking] I'm thinking about how Scala's Enumeration works when I define values like "val Red, Green, Blue = Value." It seems the compiler calls Value multiple times with nextName. I wonder if macros are needed or if there's a special case in the Scala compiler for Enumeration. 
[thinking] 
